org.apache.paimon.hive

Class PaimonSerDe

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.AbstractSerDe
      • org.apache.paimon.hive.PaimonSerDe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.Deserializer, org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.Serializer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TableStoreSerDe

    public class PaimonSerDe
extends org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.AbstractSerDe
    AbstractSerDe for paimon. It transforms map-reduce values to Hive objects.

    Currently this class only supports deserialization.
